txt.en: The Elf-scout Miluimil has been charged with capturing the creature named Gollum to prevent him from falling into the hands of the Orcs.
'Quickly! We must be away from this place!'
Speak with Miluimil and proceed into the caverns to stop the Orcs pursuing Gollum from capturing him.
'Quickly! We must be away from this place!'
Talk to Miluimil to depart from the dark caverns.
'Quickly! I can hear Orkish voices echoing from somewhere deep within these caves.\n\n'We must find them before they find Gollum!'
